id=onyx-camera-fix
name=Redmi Turbo 4 Pro Camera Fix
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=Samiul Basir Fahim
description=Fixes non-functional cameras on Global/India ROMs for Redmi Turbo 4 Pro units manufactured with second-batch hardware (AAC IMX882, Sunny OV08F, Sunny OV20B40 sensors). These units ship with CN-only vendor drivers that Global/India firmware omits, causing all cameras to fail at HAL initialization. This module systemlessly injects the missing _ii sensor module and tuning blobs into the vendor partition overlay and patches SELinux policy to allow the camera HAL to load them. No system partition is modified. Safe to uninstall.
